name: Indiana A ti
description:
An embedding of Ann Glazyrina, known in her glamor modeling days as Indiana (and occasionally as Angelica B or Anna Raise).

Indi has adorable freckles, but some models handle that better than others. If you keep seeing red or brown spots that look like acne or weird scars, try throwing "freckles" into the negative prompt.

Negative embeddings can impact your character TIs; keep that in mind. Lykon's Fast Negative is about as safe as they come in that regard. It does a great job cleaning up and has minimal to no impact on style. I use it a lot.
